{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8913b788-f945-580d-9f59-b73efc824516","excerpt":"期待已久的 Kobo Libra H2O 來啦！！！ 參加「KaLUG 1906 聚會: E-ink 大亂鬥、初探 Jetson Nano…","html":"<p>期待已久的 Kobo Libra H2O 來啦！！！</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>參加「KaLUG 1906 聚會: E-ink 大亂鬥、初探 Jetson Nano 邊緣運算開發平台」的時候被大大們燒到…</p>\n<p>思考了好一陣子，一直在想到底是要花錢買實體書來讀還是要存久一點買電子紙？</p>\n<p>後來得到結輪：電子紙方便攜帶、可以跟家人共用、電子檔容易保存、受不了了好想買(誤)</p>\n<p>半個月前預購的，原本預計到貨日期是 10/10，沒想到提早拿到了 :D</p>\n<h3>保護殼+本體</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1ff783337d3a47b6ffeb62854422de87/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kobo libra h2o 0\"\n        title=\"kobo libra h2o 0\"\n        src=\"/static/1ff783337d3a47b6ffeb62854422de87/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1ff783337d3a47b6ffeb62854422de87/5dceb/kobo-libra-h2o-0.jpg 180w,\n/static/1ff783337d3a47b6ffeb62854422de87/cfda3/kobo-libra-h2o-0.jpg 360w,\n/static/1ff783337d3a47b6ffeb62854422de87/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-0.jpg 720w,\n/static/1ff783337d3a47b6ffeb62854422de87/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-0.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Kobo 外盒</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6e2ef388a9795e9c9109279dd5758b86/4c2ca/kobo-libra-h2o-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kobo libra h2o 1\"\n        title=\"kobo libra h2o 1\"\n        src=\"/static/6e2ef388a9795e9c9109279dd5758b86/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6e2ef388a9795e9c9109279dd5758b86/5dceb/kobo-libra-h2o-1.jpg 180w,\n/static/6e2ef388a9795e9c9109279dd5758b86/cfda3/kobo-libra-h2o-1.jpg 360w,\n/static/6e2ef388a9795e9c9109279dd5758b86/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-1.jpg 720w,\n/static/6e2ef388a9795e9c9109279dd5758b86/1f304/kobo-libra-h2o-1.jpg 1080w,\n/static/6e2ef388a9795e9c9109279dd5758b86/4c2ca/kobo-libra-h2o-1.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>開箱！Kobo Libra H2O 靜靜的躺在盒子裡</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4ac4215161269aa365b2eebc6089cf68/4c2ca/kobo-libra-h2o-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kobo libra h2o 2\"\n        title=\"kobo libra h2o 2\"\n        src=\"/static/4ac4215161269aa365b2eebc6089cf68/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4ac4215161269aa365b2eebc6089cf68/5dceb/kobo-libra-h2o-2.jpg 180w,\n/static/4ac4215161269aa365b2eebc6089cf68/cfda3/kobo-libra-h2o-2.jpg 360w,\n/static/4ac4215161269aa365b2eebc6089cf68/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-2.jpg 720w,\n/static/4ac4215161269aa365b2eebc6089cf68/1f304/kobo-libra-h2o-2.jpg 1080w,\n/static/4ac4215161269aa365b2eebc6089cf68/4c2ca/kobo-libra-h2o-2.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>底下還有一條 Micro USB 線</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cd7ce5d8986e5618109382bca3bd3275/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kobo libra h2o 3\"\n        title=\"kobo libra h2o 3\"\n        src=\"/static/cd7ce5d8986e5618109382bca3bd3275/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cd7ce5d8986e5618109382bca3bd3275/5dceb/kobo-libra-h2o-3.jpg 180w,\n/static/cd7ce5d8986e5618109382bca3bd3275/cfda3/kobo-libra-h2o-3.jpg 360w,\n/static/cd7ce5d8986e5618109382bca3bd3275/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-3.jpg 720w,\n/static/cd7ce5d8986e5618109382bca3bd3275/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-3.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>試試手感，讚讚的！</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5436380f68d946a9222c172089ad0157/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kobo libra h2o 4\"\n        title=\"kobo libra h2o 4\"\n        src=\"/static/5436380f68d946a9222c172089ad0157/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5436380f68d946a9222c172089ad0157/5dceb/kobo-libra-h2o-4.jpg 180w,\n/static/5436380f68d946a9222c172089ad0157/cfda3/kobo-libra-h2o-4.jpg 360w,\n/static/5436380f68d946a9222c172089ad0157/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-4.jpg 720w,\n/static/5436380f68d946a9222c172089ad0157/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-4.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>跟我的 Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon 合體！</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/71ed5f3726ad6c0eb0e4158877c42fdc/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kobo libra h2o 5\"\n        title=\"kobo libra h2o 5\"\n        src=\"/static/71ed5f3726ad6c0eb0e4158877c42fdc/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/71ed5f3726ad6c0eb0e4158877c42fdc/5dceb/kobo-libra-h2o-5.jpg 180w,\n/static/71ed5f3726ad6c0eb0e4158877c42fdc/cfda3/kobo-libra-h2o-5.jpg 360w,\n/static/71ed5f3726ad6c0eb0e4158877c42fdc/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-5.jpg 720w,\n/static/71ed5f3726ad6c0eb0e4158877c42fdc/2fb62/kobo-libra-h2o-5.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>在 Ubuntu 上無痛使用 <a href=\"https://calibre-ebook.com/\">Calibre</a> 轉檔並上傳中</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce9d8995d5c3ccc1cfd87b88a64f220b/4c2ca/kobo-libra-h2o-6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kobo libra h2o 6\"\n        title=\"kobo libra h2o 6\"\n        src=\"/static/ce9d8995d5c3ccc1cfd87b88a64f220b/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce9d8995d5c3ccc1cfd87b88a64f220b/5dceb/kobo-libra-h2o-6.jpg 180w,\n/static/ce9d8995d5c3ccc1cfd87b88a64f220b/cfda3/kobo-libra-h2o-6.jpg 360w,\n/static/ce9d8995d5c3ccc1cfd87b88a64f220b/98007/kobo-libra-h2o-6.jpg 720w,\n/static/ce9d8995d5c3ccc1cfd87b88a64f220b/1f304/kobo-libra-h2o-6.jpg 1080w,\n/static/ce9d8995d5c3ccc1cfd87b88a64f220b/4c2ca/kobo-libra-h2o-6.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>原本用 apt 裝的 Calibre 一直抓不到 Kobo，後來去<a href=\"https://calibre-ebook.com/download\">官網下載最新版</a>就沒問題了，</p>\n<p>書的管理好簡單且閱讀體驗真的超讚的，有點相見恨晚啊 QQ</p>\n<p>接下來就是好好來閱讀一下我想讀很久的 :P</p>\n<hr>\n<p>另外低調附上好擼友推薦的 gen.lib.rus.ec</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"E Ink: Kobo Libra H2O 開箱","date":"October 01, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/e-ink-kobo-libra-h2o/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/cli-log-parsing-cool/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"面對 Log 檔的思路"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/gatsby-framework/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby Framework"}}}}